{
  "stem": "20021.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Two weeks passed by, and then, they came and gave us the bad news.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Unfortunately, somebody got interested in that case too much, and he lost his power.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He doesn't have the decision anymore, so he's afraid to release you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He's responsible for you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And looked very bad, because they finally officially-- and really, the fact of later, we were supposed to be brought back to the border.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But not to the Hungarian border, but to the Romanian-Polish border, and handed over to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the night before we left, the women of that town, really, they made a big dinner, brought a big cake, a chocolate cake.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I remember that like they had fish and everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And came to jail and cried and cried, they cried and cried.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was a terribly emotional scene.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the next day morning, we got up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we went on our way back to the border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was a long journey because we were close to the Hungarian border, but quite far from the Polish border.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And by foot, each day we would walk like maybe, oh, 10 miles or 15 miles, whatever.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Go to another jail.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Sleep overnight.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Get up in the morning, go another 15 miles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Go to another jail, sleep, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But each time at that jail, the-- the jailer's wife would cheat us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was, as a matter of fact, so mean, she had pigs there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was showing us-- the good food, I leave for the pigs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But for you Jews, that's enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was only once.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But most of the time we were fed lousy food, but fed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And just kept dragging and dragging, and got finally to the border.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
